data.description: This 3/2.5 HEATED POOL home is the epitome of luxury, on 2 LOTS, privacy fencing with NO DEED RESTRICTIONS has a new price! NEW ROOF 2023, NEW AC 2015, and HURRICANE PROTECTION ALL AROUND! This magnificent property is nestled on a sprawling DOUBLE LOT, offering an unparalleled sense of beauty and exclusivity, where every detail has been meticulously curated to create a lavish retreat. As you approach the property, you'll be captivated by the stunning facade, exuding both comfort and style. The recent addition of a NEW ROOF not only enhances the overall aesthetic but also ensures long-lasting durability and protection. A symphony of fabulous furnishings, tasteful decor, this home has an abundance of natural light welcoming you into each impeccably appointed room. As you step inside, you are greeted by the open and spacious floor plan. The living areas provides a comfortable space to relax and unwind, tall vaulted and double tray ceilings with pocket sliders plus split bedrooms sure to capture your heart.  The kitchen is a true culinary haven, featuring stainless appliances, beautiful cabinetry and backsplash, breakfast bar, plus breakfast nook with aquarium glass to pool/yard view and corian counters. Whether you're a seasoned chef or just enjoy cooking for loved ones, this well-designed kitchen is sure to impress with plenty of ambient lighting to suite any mood. Offering a peaceful retreat after a long day, the spacious master suite is a perfect private sanctuary featuring big  dual closets ,an ensuite bathroom with Roman shower & soaking tub. Each guest bedroom boasts generous space, allowing for upscale furnishings and personalization.  From the high-end finishes to the meticulous craftsmanship, every aspect of this home exudes Florida quality living with coastal ambience.  Venture outside to discover your personal oasis. The focal point of the expansive fenced backyard is a mesmerizing pebbletec pool, with its sheik private resort feel complete with solar trimmed cage, inviting you to indulge day or night in a refreshing swim or simply unwind by the water's edge. Whether hosting extravagant parties or enjoying intimate gatherings, the pool area promises endless opportunities with privacy for creating lasting memories. And there is much more with an extra unforgettable half pool bath, tiki styled your guests will absolutely fall in love with. Wired for a generator, inside laundry room, convenient accordian hurricane shutters, irrigation, manibloc plumbing and extra features of bedroom lighting just adds to the custom extras to fully appreciate and enjoy.This home is conveniently situated near amenities such as parks, schools, and shopping centers. Enjoy the convenience of nearby attractions while still being able to retreat to your peaceful oasis. Offering a delightful living experience with its charming interior, well-appointed kitchen, comfortable bedrooms, pool oasis, extra yard space and tranquility, don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home. Contact us today to arrange a viewing!
